data.description: Brand New Home!! Upgrades galore! New kitchen is a chef's dream with plenty of cabinets, modernized stainless steel appliance package. Two New Tiled bathrooms that await you. Four large bedrooms have upgraded new carpet. Large living room is refined with laminate flooring. Home is freshly painted. Many special enhancements include recessed lighting, ceiling fans, chair rail and show box molding. Many other upgrades to include new ac and washer and dryer. Beautiful and professionally landscaped and large back yard. Many other extras that you must tour this lovely home to see. Super clean garage for storage or pulling your car in for those cold nights. 2018 The Year of Home Ownership!! Blue Light Special! Priced For Quick Sale! Open House Everyday Until Sold!!
